commitResults.messageTitle: Abstract out the bye command into CommandByeHandler.java.
commitResults.messageBody:
Previously, the bye command is checked at the user input level.
This is not ideal because the implementation is not extensible.

By capitalizing on the previously built infrastructure of CommandHandler,
I abstracted out the bye command into its own class to have better
extensibility and overall cleanliness of the code.

commitResults.messageTitle: Fix bug where index out of bounds exception is not caught correctly.
commitResults.messageBody:
When user tries to mark or delete a task that is out of bounds,
the exception is not caught correctly.
Added junit tests that specifically test this so that we do not encounter such issues in the future.
